sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FastAPI as vllm-openai FastAPI<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Auth as AuthenticationMiddleware<br/>API Key (SHA-256)
    participant Engine as vLLM AsyncEngine (V1)<br/>In-process
    participant Executor as Model Executor/Worker<br/>CPU (PyTorch)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Engine,HFHub: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup
        Engine->>HFHub: GET model weights & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HFHub-->>Engine: Model artifacts
        Engine->>Engine: Write to local filesystem
        Engine->>Executor: Load model into memory<br/>In-process
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over Client,Executor: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (OpenAI API)
        Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        KServe->>FastAPI: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
        FastAPI->>Auth: Validate API key<br/>Constant-time SHA-256 comparison
        Auth-->>FastAPI: Authenticated
        FastAPI->>Engine: Inference request<br/>In-process (async)
        Engine->>Executor: Schedule execution<br/>In-process
        Executor->>Executor: PyTorch CPU inference<br/>(IPEX/OpenBLAS acceleration)
        Executor-->>Engine: Token generation
        Engine-->>FastAPI: Streaming tokens
        FastAPI-->>KServe: SSE stream or JSON response<br/>HTTP/8000
        KServe-->>Client: HTTPS response<br/>TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over Client,Executor: Flow 3: gRPC Inference (TGIS Adapter)
        participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

        Client->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationService<br/>8033/TCP, Configurable TLS
        TGIS->>Engine: Inference request<br/>In-process
        Engine->>Executor: Schedule execution<br/>In-process
        Executor->>Executor: PyTorch CPU inference
        Executor-->>Engine: Generated tokens
        Engine-->>TGIS: Token stream
        TGIS-->>Client: gRPC streaming response<br/>8033/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over FastAPI,FastAPI: Observability
        participant Prom as Prometheus

        Prom->>FastAPI: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000
        FastAPI-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
        Prom->>FastAPI: GET /health<br/>HTTP/8000
        FastAPI-->>Prom: Health status
    end
